  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Colorgrid</strong> is a puzzle game about mixing colors in a Lab.  Find the correct positions for your lasers and mirrors to get the right mix of colors in each material.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>70 hand-crafted levels</strong> with increasing complexity;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Originally composed music</strong> to help you focus and relax while solving the puzzles;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Learn the basics of <strong>color mixing</strong> to solve the levels.</p></li></ul>",
